author: Patrick Cc:
description:
Katy Perry was once the bold, rebellious face of pop music. But behind the candy-coated image was a persona built more for mass appeal rather than authenticity. This video breaks down how her rise, fall, and recent controversies exposed a pop star who never truly stood for anything.
